Hold on.

24
00:01:54,870 --> 00:01:55,760
Skip the Plain Noodles.

25
00:01:56,070 --> 00:01:56,840
Make it two bowls of

26
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:58,070
smelly bamboo shoot noodles.

27
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,280
- Got it.
- Smelly...

28
00:01:59,950 --> 00:02:01,000
bamboo shoot noodles?

29
00:02:01,440 --> 00:02:02,310
Mm.

30
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:05,120
What we usually have
are elixirs and delicacies.

31
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,310
But now we're in Hunling City.

32
00:02:06,310 --> 00:02:08,520
We should try something bold.

33
00:02:10,680 --> 00:02:11,750
You've been here before?

34
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:12,800
Mm.

35
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:15,430
Immortals and demons are constantly
at war.

36
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:16,500
My spiritual power is weak.

37
00:02:16,710 --> 00:02:18,280
So I often sneak out in secret.

38
00:02:19,220 --> 00:02:20,080
Honored guests,

39
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,750
smelly bamboo shoot noodles is ready.

40
00:02:21,960 --> 00:02:23,080
Thank you.

41
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:24,920
Please enjoy it.

42
00:02:26,800 --> 00:02:28,000
Such foul-smelling stuff.

43
00:02:28,310 --> 00:02:29,150
You're not eating it?

44
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,360
Then I will.

45
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,120
You Immortal Clan folk

46
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:39,400
rarely have tastes like yours.s

47
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,560
Little rascal, still eating noodles.

48
00:02:45,560 --> 00:02:46,590
You ruined my plan.

49
00:02:47,410 --> 00:02:48,340
You…

50
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:51,680
I spared you just now.

51
00:02:51,870 --> 00:02:53,030
Yet you didn't value it.

52
00:02:53,030 --> 00:02:54,840
Then I'll make you suffer a bit.

53
00:02:55,630 --> 00:02:56,470
Come on, then.

54
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,680
This is my own Heaven Formation.

55
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:04,560
Today, I'll let you witness it.

56
00:03:12,710 --> 00:03:14,080
You're done now, huh?

57
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,800
Sorry, Your Grace. I'm counting on you.

58
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:17,640
Not your business.

59
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,390
(His power hasn't recovered.)

60
00:03:28,390 --> 00:03:29,710
(But he should be fine, right?)

61
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:34,310
Run?

62
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:35,840
Hand over the money.

63
00:03:36,750 --> 00:03:37,710
I…

64
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:38,920
Go…

65
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,630
- Monster!
- Monster!

66
00:03:51,450 --> 00:03:52,310
Monster!

67
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,240
It's a monster!

68
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:56,800
No…

69
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:57,640
I'm not…

70
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,630
I'm not a monster.

71
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,860
I'm not a monster.

72
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,400
