73
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,470
I'm not a monster.

74
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,680
I'm not a monster.

75
00:04:09,150 --> 00:04:09,990
Monster!

76
00:04:11,520 --> 00:04:12,750
Strike her down!

77
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:15,840
Get lost!

78
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:17,960
Hit her!

79
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:20,800
- Strike her down!
- Burn her!

80
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,600
You troublesome succubus, a true jinx.

81
00:04:35,270 --> 00:04:37,530
Some spiritual plants in my manor
aren't planted yet.

82
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,800
I won't let you suffer any harm again.

83
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:48,520
Run, quickly!

84
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,880
Stop right there.

85
00:05:46,270 --> 00:05:47,110
Where are you going?

86
00:05:47,510 --> 00:05:48,350
Your Grace,

87
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,480
I'm taking a stroll.

88
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,270
You left me alone back there.

89
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:54,070
Yet you ran off in a flash.

90
00:05:54,540 --> 00:05:55,390
Are you afraid

91
00:05:55,390 --> 00:05:56,240
I'd settle scores?

92
00:05:56,870 --> 00:05:58,160
No, it's not that.

93
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:00,750
It's just the people in Hunling City

94
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:03,070
could never be your match, Your Grace.

95
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,310
I was only worried that

96
00:06:04,310 --> 00:06:05,510
I'd slow you down in a fight.

97
00:06:11,390 --> 00:06:12,130
With the scales,

98
00:06:12,130 --> 00:06:13,390
you can't go anywhere unnoticed.

99
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,480
You're eternal and indestructible.

100
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:19,800
Power beyond measure.

101
00:06:20,600 --> 00:06:21,860
I'm just an Immortal Beast,

102
00:06:21,860 --> 00:06:22,720
wounded and weary.

103
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:25,000
Unlike you, I can't recover instantly.

104
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:27,480
I don't want others to see me like this.

105
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,070
Even an Immortal Beast has pride.

106
00:06:30,430 --> 00:06:31,270
I don't think

107
00:06:31,430 --> 00:06:32,270
you look bad.

108
00:06:36,310 --> 00:06:37,160
I just feel

109
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:39,120
it's a bit conspicuous.

110
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,510
Since I was the one who took you out,

111
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,040
I would never

112
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,120
hold it against you.

113
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,680
If those scales on you

114
00:06:48,920 --> 00:06:49,760
trouble you,

115
00:06:50,270 --> 00:06:51,600
I have a way to resolve it.

116
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:52,710
Really?

117
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,770
Yes.

118
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:54,710
I mean it.

